 one of them likely to invite you to supper as anything but the main course,
 if you know what I mean.}
{141}{}{垃圾镇外面还有什么？}
{142}{}{谢谢。}
{143}{Kill09}{Well, ya got the Hub southwest. Don't go south, though. That'd be Necropolis;
